{"tid":1359902,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[遍地開花][整合]各界公開信 歡迎自貼 (但請大家不要忘記初心係五大訴求)","createTime":"2019-07-24T08:39:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T04:00:35.000Z","uid":39085,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"21b9bdc01cd7e4d8a5fb0f377aac19788c1e5710","tid":1359902,"uid":39085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T08:39:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">有見及政府各部門, 各界都發起了不同聲明, 我係呢度開個整合post, 如果你/你同事/你朋友/你家人 係各界別而又想發聲, 亦歡迎自貼! 最後再做一個大整合<br />\n另外, 有不少界別只有一張或數張員工卡, 希望大家share出去, <span style=\"color: red;\">讓不同界別力量集中起來</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>但同時, 請大家不要再過分集中遍地開花, 焦點依然係五大訴求, 係727, 728既遊行集會</strong><br />\n要推番有用資訊上熱門post!<br />\n<br />\n最最最重要係, 大家要牢牢記住:<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">1. 巴打整合 超過百人</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">[遍地開花] 跨 部 門 公 務 員 致 香 港 人 的 公 開 信<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1359384/page/7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1359384/page/7</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">2. 航空界別</span> <strong>請大家支持726機場集會!</strong><br />\n[繼續開花] 到我地機師做野喇<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1359574/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1359574/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n（遍地開花）到民航處空管人員做嘢啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1358986/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1358986/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n［遍地開花］ 到我地CPSL做嘢喇 (國泰)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1359618/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1359618/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: maroon;\">3. 社會各專業界別</span><br />\n[遍地開花] 建築測量業界致全港市民書<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1359523/page/2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1359523/page/2</a><br />\n<br />\n[遍地開花] 到我地香港工程師做野喇！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1359394/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1359394/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n［遍地開花］建造業既你地 仲唔出黎？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1359580/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1359580/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n[遍地開花] 職訓局職員公開信<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1359743/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1359743/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n[遍地開花]社會福利署出現連儂牆！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1359532/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1359532/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\">4. 救護界別</span><br />\n(遍地開花)到我地聖約翰救傷隊做野啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1358671/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1358671/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n(遍地開花)今次到我地醫療輔助隊有野講<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1359458/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1359458/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">5. 反仆街cctvb 界別</span><br />\n［遍地開花，歡迎報料］TVB員工譴責TVB報假新聞<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1359321/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1359321/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\nTVB 員工做野啦（附上員工證）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1359444/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1359444/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">6. 政府部門各界別</span><br />\n（遍地開花）到我地渠務署做野啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1359640/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1359640/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n（遍地開花）到我地水務署做野啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1359279/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1359279/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n(遍地開花）到我地房署做野啦 （轉載）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1359062/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1359062/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n[繼續開花] 海關職員加入響應 支持香港人<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1357160/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1357160/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n(遍地開花）到我地懲教做野啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1357204/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1357204/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n［遍地開花］年輕紀律部隊要爬山 (入境)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1354244/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1354244/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n[遍地開花]反了！到政府總部同事爬山<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1355968/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1355968/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n[遍地開花] 文書及秘書職系公務員致全港市民書<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1358989/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1358989/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n（遍地開花）借ac開 機電工程署兄弟出黎啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1359188/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1359188/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n[遍地開花]機電工程署及渠務署員工致香港市民<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1359766/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1359766/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n(遍地開花）運輸署有人做嘢啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1359757/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1359757/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n【遍地開花】漁護署同事致香港人<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1359738/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1359738/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n[遍地開花] 連最仆街嘅食環署都作反啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1359320/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1359320/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n[遍地開花] 到我地建築署做野啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1359872/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1359872/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\">7. 交通界別</span><br />\n［遍地開花］集合港鐵員工反黑社會反黑警力量<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1359498/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1359498/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n遍地開花 - 一位資深的交通安全隊義工<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1359224/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1359224/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n【遍地開花】九巴員工反對警黑勾結<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1359841/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1359841/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"4602b42ab003b82526649ea34be6aad966efb8aa","tid":1359902,"uid":266805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T08:40:17.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"2cab5380425e951568bc21affad3c2dc2d6b1664","tid":1359902,"uid":239210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T08:41:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"76a3a7b822155da3d019c8d5b57ca2618d621e1a","tid":1359902,"uid":266805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T08:41:09.000Z","msg":"[遍地開花] 我地救護員都要做野<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1359906\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1359906</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"031264650bd3376beb2bcba4d77199b7ed5bb7aa","tid":1359902,"uid":39085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T08:41:32.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命<br />\n727 728見!"},{"pid":"03bebf6ec7f86a383550f286d01eddd38fd7da0f","tid":1359902,"uid":39085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T08:42:05.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命<br />\n727 728見!"},{"pid":"53f9605d59a0e5d24d9389e69c10215c04b6dd30","tid":1359902,"uid":39085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T08:42:36.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命<br />\n727 728見!"},{"pid":"d9168448a969392fa1d5a5fe434978f552b6c1ef","tid":1359902,"uid":177679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T08:45:25.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命<br />\n727 728見!"},{"pid":"23813d8ef6557a34ae7c0609a09b5f2ab373b3cc","tid":1359902,"uid":39085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cit